SWS Website System
==================

The "SWS Website System", is an Erlang program to server simple websites. It
uses Basho's Webmachine as it's webserver and the Django template language
(Evan Miller's ErlyDTL) for rendering the webpages.


Compiling
---------

$ ./rebar compile

or

$ ./rebar compile eunit

to run the unit tests.


Usage
-----

Place routes for your resources in priv/dispatch.conf. Add the page templates
in priv/templates/, web pages in priv/pages/, stylesheets in priv/lib/css/,
javascripts in priv/lib/js/ and files in priv/files/.

Modify sws.sh with your settings and start the application with:

# ./sws.sh start


